settings.product_description:
Our Shred Program is a no-nonsense blueprint for anyone keen to shed the extra kgs, build lean muscle, and overhaul their lifestyle.

The program incorporates a 4 day training split, full macro breakdown with meal guides and daily accountability from your coaches to ensure you are on track to lose those stubborn Kg's and redefine your physique.

This program is for anyone trying to build size and increase muscle mass. If you’ve always struggled to put on size this is a great option for you. We have had 100’s of blokes get great results.

The program incorporates a 4 day training split, full macro breakdown with meal guides and daily accountability from your coaches to ensure you are on track to building a bigger, stronger physique.

settings.title: What is the 12-week program?
settings.text:
Our 12-week program, available in 'Shred' or 'Build' options, is tailor-made to meet your individual goals. The program includes a personalised training regime, meal guide, macro breakdown, and daily accountability checks to help you reach your objectives and lead a healthier lifestyle.

Shred: This program is designed to eliminate unwanted body fat using a macro breakdown and a 4-day training program. You'll receive a macro breakdown, meal guide, daily accountability check-ins, and weekly phone call check-ins with progress photos.

Build: This program aims at muscle gain while also shedding unwanted body fat, with a macro breakdown and a 4-day training program. It includes a macro breakdown, meal guide, daily accountability check-ins, and weekly phone call check-ins with progress photos.

settings.title: Who is the Real Bodz program for?
settings.text: The Real Bodz program is designed for men grappling with weight issues, lifestyle habits, and mental health. It's for those eager to transform their bodies and their lives. If you are not actually ready to change, then don't bother with our programs. We want to work with people are ready to do the hard work to achieve their goals.

settings.title: What will I need before buying?
settings.text: Before joining the program, all you need is a positive mindset and readiness to commit to changing your daily lifestyle habits. You'll also need a smartphone to access the apps and communicate with your coach.

settings.title: Do I need access to a gym?
settings.text: No, gym access is not necessary. During our initial consultation, we will determine whether an at-home or gym training program best fits your goals.

settings.title: What are the next steps after purchase?
settings.text: Post-purchase, you will receive an onboarding email that includes a PDF guide outlining the entire process. This guide will detail the apps to use, how to set them up, and what to expect in the coming weeks.

settings.title: What if I don’t see any results?
settings.text:
We guarantee results! We are results driven and offer a money-back guarantee if you don’t see results after the 12 program. We know our programs work and are willing to back it with our own time and money.

The more communication you have with your coach and the better adherence you have to your plans, the greater your results will be.
